Toxic Comments classification
Exploratory Data Analysis

Purpose- To distinguish between toxic comments and pure intention comments. 
The goal is not to judge the comments but to prevents unnecessary consequences.

How- Language Classification

Human Language is so complex. 
Let start with English Language. 
English Language combines with sentences, words and punctuations.

Comments classifies to fields as sentences counts, words count and punctuations. 
And then a fields that classified that toxic words with common words.

Than do the exploratory data analysis.
